ComicInfo.Summary: The Wine-Dark Deep [Part 2]: On the planet I'Qos, war has broken out between the I'Qosa and Lo'Kari, with Spock, Sulu, and Chekov caught in the middle. When Speaker Bryni is killed, Ayal steps in to lead the I'Qosa. When Spock and the away team return to the Enterprise, Sulu bids a tearful farewell to Ayal.
